Invocation Name: greenwood elections
des: Students at Greenwood Elementary can ask their Alexa or Echo who they should vote for in the upcoming student council elections and will receive a response that they should vote for Ally for president of the SCA. My 5th grade daughter is learning about coding by teaching Alexa a skill that can be used by fellow students at her elementary school for the upcoming student council elections.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
